ETAPI_OPENAPI_REQ.DESCRIPTION:
You must take the ID of the column that the user wants to be of type list and you must modify the "reference" parameter to "17" and in the "referenceSearchKey" parameter you must put the ID of the reference that the user passed you.
Example of the call:
{'url': 'http://tomcat:8080/etendo', 'endpoint': '/sws/com.etendoerp.etendorx.datasource/ChangeColumn/"ID of the column type list"', 'method': 'PUT', 'body_params': '{"reference":"17","referenceSearchKey":"REFERENCE ID"}', 'query_params': None, 'token': 'ETENDO_TOKEN'}
